So the Joint Chiefs
were not including

00:38:56.240 --> 00:38:59.840
the main casualty-producing
effect of thermonuclear weapons

00:38:59.840 --> 00:39:02.220
when they said 600 million.

00:39:02.220 --> 00:39:05.660
Fire not included, just
prompt radiation, blast,

00:39:05.660 --> 00:39:06.900
immediate heat and so forth.

